        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_RECOLOR1_COMMANDO_NAME": "Commando: Scorpion",
        "SS2_PYRO_SCORCH_DESCRIPTION": "<color=#D78326>升温</color>通过<style=cIsDamage>燃烧附近的敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>60%伤害</style>。用<color=#D78326>高温</color><style=cIsDamage>ignites</style>攻击敌人,造成<style=cIsDamage>持续伤害</style>。",
