        "SS2_EXECUTIONER2_CONSECRATION_DESC": "消耗所有<color=#29e5f2>离子充能</color>进行<style=cIsHealing>治疗</style>,获得<style=cIsUtility>移动速度</style>提升,且每点充能减少<style=cIsUtility>1秒</style>技能冷却。",
