        "SS2_ARTIFACT_COGNATION_NAME": "衍生神器",
        "SS2_ITEM_JETBOOTS_DESC": "获得<style=cIsUtility>一次额外跳跃次数</style>,可<style=cIsDamage>点燃</style><style=cIsDamage>{1}米</style><style=cStack>(每层+{2}米)</style>半径内的敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>{0}%</style>基础伤害,落地后<style=cIsUtility>{3}</style>秒重新充能",
