        "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_75_DECREASE_BODY_TOKEN": "玩家承受25%伤害。",
        "SS2_TRADER_CONTEXT": "讨价还价?",
        "SS2_NEMMANDO_OUTRO_FLAVOR": "……于是他离开了,怀抱着新生的人性之光。",
        "SS2_SKIN_CAPTAIN_GRANDMASTERY": "声望",
        "SS2_PYRO_OUTRO_FAILURE": "..于是他消失了,火焰熄灭了。",
