        "SS2_DIFFICULTY_TEMPEST2_NAME": "风暴+2",
        "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_GOOLAKE": "大门的景色。",
        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMCOMMANDO_BOSSATTACK_DESC": "As Nemesis Commando, apply 8 or more stacks of Gouge to a single target at once.",
        "SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_NAME": "灭绝遗物",
        "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_75_DECREASE_NAME_TOKEN": "-75%受到的伤害",
        "SS2_TRADER_POPUP_TEXT": "向交易商提供物品?",
        "SS2_WARDEN_BODY_LORE": "为什么太空里会有典狱长",
        "SS2_ITEM_SKATEBOARD_NAME": "迅捷滑板",
        "SS2_CHIRR_NAME": "奇尔",
        "SS2_BIRTHRIGHT_OBJECTIVE": "尚有{0}项<style=cIsUtility>继承权</style>未领取。",
        "SS2_UNLOCKABLE_LOG_LAMP": "Logbook: Follower",
        "SS2_PYRO_AIRBLAST_DESCRIPTION": "<color=#D78326>30%热量</color>。发射一团火焰,<color=#D78326>点燃</color>敌人,造成<style=cIsDamage>400%伤害</style>并<style=cIsUtility>反弹投射物</style>额外层数<color=#D78326>减少15%的热量消耗</color>.",
        "SS2_NEMCOMMANDO_NAME": "复仇指挥官",
        "SS2_ARTIFACT_HAVOC_DESC": "事件发生更早且更频繁。暴风雨永久存在。",
        "SS2_RULEBOOK_EMPTY": "未找到可自定义的规则!",
        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SLIDE_DESC": "As Nemesis Mercenary, complete a stage without leaving the ground.",
        "SS2_EQUIP_WHITEFLAG_DESC": "放置一面白旗,使<style=cIsUtility>{0}米</style>内的单位<style=cIsUtility>无法使用技能</style>,持续<style=cIsUtility>{1}秒</style>。",
        "SS2_AGARTHAN_BODY_NAME": "雅戈泰",
        "SS2_ITEM_SHACKLEDLAMP_PICKUP": "每使用5次主要技能,发射一个鬼魂。",
        "SS2_EQUIP_MIDAS_LORE": "\"这是什么意思?\"\n\n他们都在想这件事,但她是第一个问出来的。\n\n\"我……美妙的一天开始了?\" 他笑了。\n\n\"孟菲斯再次濒死斯蒂芬\"\n\n\"线粒体在六点被击败\"\n\n\"殡葬业者无视死亡叹息\"\n\n\"真有……诗意。\"他挠了挠下巴。\"想打开吗?\"\n\n\"该死……还是算了。\"",
        "SS2_ITEM_UNIVERSALCHARGER_LORE": "支持UESB-A至UESB-ZZ等……",
        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_HOTTESTSAUCE_DESC": "Carry a Kjaro's Band, Gasoline, and Will-o'-the-wisp all at once.",
        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_DIARY_DESC": "Reach level 20.",
        "SS2_ITEM_MALICE_DESC": "命中时对{0}米内<style=cIsDamage>{1}</style> <style=cStack>(每层+{1})</style>个敌人造成<style=cIsDamage>{2}%</style>的伤害。",
        "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_25_INCREASE_BODY_TOKEN": "玩家承受125%伤害。",
        "SS2_ITEM_DROIDHEAD_NAME": "机器人头颅",
        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_BLOODTESTER_DESC": "Heal for 5,000 health in a single run.",
        "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SECONDARY_KNIFE_DESCRIPTION": "<style=cIsHealth>流血。</style>投掷一把刀造成<style=cIsDamage>100%伤害</style>。\n<style=cIsDamage>屠戮者。</style>靠近后将其拔出,造成<style=cIsDamage>400%伤害</style>。",
        "SS2_ITEM_SHIELDGATE_LORE": "???",
        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_MALICE_NAME": "Malicious",
        "SS2_CHIRR_GRAB_NAME": "绑架",
        "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_LORE": "???",
        "SS2_ACHIEVEMENT_NEMMANDO_NAME": "Lone Echo",
        "SS2_ITEM_CRYPTICSOURCE_PICKUP": "奔跑会积蓄伤害性能量爆发。",
        "SS2_ITEM_CRYPTICSOURCE_NAME": "秘源棱晶",
        "SS2_ITEM_DROIDHEAD_LORE": "运单:安保机器人\r\n单号:1138****\r\n预计送达时间:05/14/2056\r\n运送方式:优先、易碎品 \r\n送货地址:火星,阿西莫夫,拉卡姆机器人中心\r\n运单详情:\n\n这是我们从被盗的机器人中搜到的为数不多完整器件之一……冥王星上的激进分子偷了一大堆ER-14,在他们的基地用了好一会儿了。具体地说这台是ER-14XPC5VVUFF,就像你记得的那样。我不知道之前发生了什么,我只知道找到这批残骸能拿到大笔的赏金。还有其他的残骸,不过远不如这个完整……至少不会给人造成危险。如果你也要那些的话,请联系我。\n",
        "SS2_DRONE_SHOCK_DESCRIPTION": "一种用金钱购买的同伴,会近距离跟随幸存者,<style=cIsUtility>电击</style>敌人,打断并眩晕它们。",
        "SS2_PLAYER_ARMOR_100_INCREASE_BODY_TOKEN": "玩家承受200%伤害。",
        "SS2_ITEM_DETRITIVETREMATODE_PICKUP": "低生命值敌人将持续受到伤害。",
        "SS2_EQUIP_BACKTHRUSTER_DESC": "在{0}秒内,当以直线路径移动时,快速获得最多<style=cIsUtility>{1}移动速度加成</style>。",
        "SS2_CHIRR_DROP_DESCRIPTION": "释放被擒目标,在着陆时造成<style=cIsDamage>1500%范围伤害</style>。",
        "SS2_ITEM_COMPOSITEINJECTOR_NAME": "组合式喷头",
        "SS2_ITEM_RAINBOWROOT_NAME": "虹彩源质",
        "SS2_PLAYER_DAMAGE_50_INCREASE_BODY_TOKEN": "玩家造成150%伤害。",
        "SS2_NEMMANDO_SPECIAL_SUBMISSION_NAME": "压制射击",
        "SS2_CHIRRHELPER_NAME": "奇尔的友谊",
        "SS2_EVENT_FOG_START": "浓雾逐渐升起……",
        "SS2_ITEM_FORK_LORE": "\"你逗我呢…… 听着,我确实说过我们需要利用一切资源生存,但是我所说的一切资源绝对不包括这个!\"\n\n他举起那银色的餐具,露出了疑惑的表情。 \"你什么意思?万一我们碰到怪物怎么办?\"\n\n一阵沉默\n\n\"我真是服了,咱们都见过这个星球上的怪物了,你不会觉得这玩意儿能对怪物起什么作用吧?\"\n\n他耸了耸肩 \"谁知道呢?\",他答道,同时把叉子塞回到自己口袋里。\n",
        "SS2_ITEM_BLEEDOUT_NAME": "濒死挣扎",
        "SS2_DIFFICULTY_SUPERTYPHOON_NAME": "超强台风",
        "SS2_ITEM_SCRAPFROMCHEST_DESC": "宝箱有<style=cIsUtility>33%</style><style=cStack>(每层+11%)</style>概率掉落额外<style=cIsUtility>废料</style>。",
        "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_SUBTITLE": "与船同归",
        "SS2_ITEM_STRANGECAN_PICKUP": "概率致醉敌人,造成持续伤害。击杀致醉的敌人可回复生命。",
        "SS2_KEYWORD_ATTACKVECTOR": "<style=cKeywordName>攻击矢量</style><style=cSub>打断敌人的行动。",
        "SS2_SHRINE_ETHEREAL_HINT_WISPGRAVEYARD": "俯视着一块巨大的,闪闪发光的石头。",
        "SS2_ELITE_AFFIXGILDED_NAME": "",
        "SS2_NEMESIS_MERCENARY_SPECIAL_SCEPTER_CLONE_DESCRIPTION": "在目标身后召唤<style=cIsUtility>分身</style>,<style=cIsDamage>复制你的技能</style>。重按技能可瞬移至分身位置,造成<style=cIsDamage>800%伤害</style>。\n<color=#d299ff>权杖:获得额外突进次数</color>",
        "SS2_ITEM_DEBUFFMISSILES_LORE": "???",
