        "SS2_EQUIP_MAGNET_DESC": "将<style=cIsUtility>{0}米内</style>的可拾取物拉向自身。",
        "SS2_ITEM_UNIVERSALCHARGER_DESC": "每<style=cIsUtility>{0}秒</style><style=cStack>(每层-{1}%)</style>,立即<style=cIsUtility>刷新</style>你下一个<style=cIsUtility>非主要技能</style>的<style=cIsUtility>冷却时间</style>。",
